30→    return userBuilder.build(id, username, bio, image, password, email);\n    31→  }\n    32→\n    33→  public Tag tag(TagEntity tagEntity) {\n    34→    return tagBuilder.build(tagEntity.getId(), tagEntity.getName());\n    35→  }\n    36→\n    37→  public Tag tag(TagRelationshipEntity tagRelationshipEntity) {\n    38→    return tag(tagRelationshipEntity.getPrimaryKey().getTag());\n    39→  }\n    40→\n    41→  public Article article(ArticleEntity articleEntity) {\n    42→    return articleBuilder.build(\n    43→        articleEntity.getId(),\n    44→        articleEntity.getSlug(),\n    45→        articleEntity.getTitle(),\n    46→        articleEntity.getDescription(),\n    47→        articleEntity.getBody(),\n    48→        articleEntity.getCreatedAt(),\n    49→        articleEntity.getUpdatedAt(),\n    50→        user(articleEntity.getAuthor()));\n    51→  }\n    52→\n    53→  public Comment comment(CommentEntity commentEntity) {\n    54→    return commentBuilder.build(\n    55→        commentEntity.getId(),\n    56→        user(commentEntity.getAuthor()),\n    57→        article(commentEntity.getArticle()),\n    58→        commentEntity.getBody(),\n    59→        commentEntity.getCreatedAt(),\n    60→        commentEntity.getUpdatedAt());\n    61→  }\n    62→\n    63→  public FavoriteRelationship favoriteRelationship(\n    64→      FavoriteRelationshipEntity favoriteRelationshipEntity) {\n    65→    return new FavoriteRelationship(\n    66→        user(favoriteRelationshipEntity.getUser()),\n    67→        article(favoriteRelationshipEntity.getArticle()));\n    68→  }\n    69→}\n    70→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01VppwGm4r3QYAAJFWrTAD8a","session_id":"e551caab-c624-46bd-b50e-a080c0cd7305","uuid":"c9f57a8e-cbe7-48b8-8373-860bf0872b28"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01VppwGm4r3QYAAJFWrTAD8a","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! All 9 files have been successfully written with the migration from Panache to JPA EntityManager. Let me create a summary of what was changed:\n\n## Migration Summary\n\nI've successfully migrated all Panache repository classes to use JPA EntityManager directly. Here's what was changed across the 9 files:\n\n### 1. **AbstractPanacheRepository.java**\n**Location:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/repository/hibernate/panache/AbstractPanacheRepository.java`\n\n**Changes:**\n- Removed `implements PanacheRepositoryBase<ENTITY, ID>` and generics\n- Added `@PersistenceContext protected EntityManager entityManager`\n- Changed `getEntityManager().find()` to `entityManager.find()`\n- Kept helper methods: `findUserEntityById()`, `findTagEntityById()`, etc.\n\n### 2. **UserRepositoryPanache.java**\n**Location:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/repository/hibernate/panache/UserRepositoryPanache.java`\n\n**Changes:**\n- Replaced `@ApplicationScoped` with `@Repository`\n- Removed `extends AbstractPanacheRepository<UserEntity, UUID>`\n- Removed static imports for Panache Parameters\n- Replaced `persist()` with `entityManager.persist()`\n- Replaced `count(query, params)` with `entityManager.createQuery(..., Long.class).getSingleResult()`\n- Replaced `find().firstResultOptional()` with `entityManager.createQuery(...).getResultStream().findFirst()`\n- Replaced `findByIdOptional()` with `entityManager.find()`\n- Replaced `findById()` with `entityManager.find()`\n- Converted Panache Parameters to JPA setParameter calls\n\n### 3. **ArticleRepositoryPanache.java**\n**Location:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/repository/hibernate/panache/ArticleRepositoryPanache.java`\n\n**Changes:**\n- Replaced `@ApplicationScoped` with `@Repository`\n- Removed `extends AbstractPanacheRepository<ArticleEntity, UUID>`\n- Removed Panache Page, Sort, and Parameters imports\n- Replaced `persistAndFlush()` with `entityManager.persist()` + `entityManager.flush()`\n- Replaced `deleteById()` with `entityManager.find()` + `entityManager.remove()`\n- Replaced Panache Page pagination with `.setFirstResult()` and `.setMaxResults()`\n- Replaced Panache Sort with SQL `ORDER BY` clauses in queries\n- Changed count queries from `count(query, params)` to explicit count queries\n- Fixed count query to use `select count(distinct articles)` instead of `from ArticleEntity`\n\n### 4. **TagRepositoryPanache.java**\n**Location:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/repository/hibernate/panache/TagRepositoryPanache.java`\n\n**Changes:**\n- Replaced `@ApplicationScoped` with `@Repository`\n- Removed `extends AbstractPanacheRepository<TagEntity, UUID>`\n- Replaced `listAll()` with `entityManager.createQuery(\"from TagEntity\", TagEntity.class).getResultList()`\n- Replaced `persist()` with `entityManager.persist()`\n- Converted Panache find queries to EntityManager createQuery\n\n### 5. **CommentRepositoryPanache.java**\n**Location:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/repository/hibernate/panache/CommentRepositoryPanache.java`\n\n**Changes:**\n- Replaced `@ApplicationScoped` with `@Repository`\n- Removed `extends AbstractPanacheRepository<CommentEntity, UUID>`\n- Replaced `persist()` with `entityManager.persist()`\n- Replaced `delete(entity)` with `entityManager.remove(entity)`\n- Converted Panache Parameters to JPA setParameter\n\n### 6. **FavoriteRelationshipRepositoryPanache.java**\n**Location:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/repository/hibernate/panache/FavoriteRelationshipRepositoryPanache.java`\n\n**Changes:**\n- Replaced `@ApplicationScoped` with `@Repository`\n- Removed `extends AbstractPanacheRepository<FavoriteRelationshipEntity, FavoriteRelationshipEntityKey>`\n- Converted all count and find queries to EntityManager equivalents\n- Fixed field reference from `f.article.id` and `f.user.id` to proper entity references\n\n### 7. **FollowRelationshipRepositoryPanache.java**\n**Location:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/repository/hibernate/panache/FollowRelationshipRepositoryPanache.java`\n\n**Changes:**\n- Replaced `@ApplicationScoped` with `@Repository`\n- Removed `extends AbstractPanacheRepository<FollowRelationshipEntity, FollowRelationshipEntityKey>`\n- Replaced `persistAndFlush()` with `entityManager.persist()` + `entityManager.flush()`\n- Replaced `find(\"primaryKey\", key).firstResultOptional()` with `entityManager.find()` using composite key\n- Replaced `delete(entity)` with `entityManager.remove(entity)`\n\n### 8. **TagRelationshipRepositoryPanache.java**\n**Location:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/repository/hibernate/panache/TagRelationshipRepositoryPanache.java`\n\n**Changes:**\n- Replaced `@ApplicationScoped` with `@Repository`\n- Removed `extends AbstractPanacheRepository<TagRelationshipEntity, TagRelationshipEntityKey>`\n- Replaced `persist()` with `entityManager.persist()`\n- Converted Panache find queries to EntityManager createQuery\n\n### 9. **EntityUtils.java**\n**Location:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/repository/hibernate/entity/EntityUtils.java`\n\n**Changes:**\n- Replaced `@ApplicationScoped` with `@Component`\n- No other changes to the class logic\n\n## Key Migration Patterns Applied:\n\n1. **Annotation changes:** `@ApplicationScoped` → `@Repository` (or `@Component` for EntityUtils)\n2. **Inheritance:** Removed generics from AbstractPanacheRepository\n3. **Persistence operations:** `persist()` → `entityManager.persist()`\n4. **Query operations:** `find()` → `entityManager.createQuery()`\n5. **Count operations:** `count()` → `entityManager.createQuery(..., Long.class).getSingleResult()`\n6. **Delete operations:** `deleteById()` or `delete()` → `entityManager.find()` + `entityManager.remove()`\n7. **Pagination:** Panache Page → `.setFirstResult()` and `.setMaxResults()`\n8. **Sorting:** Panache Sort → SQL `ORDER BY` in query strings\n9. **Parameters:** Panache Parameters.with() → `.setParameter()`\n10. **Results:** `.firstResultOptional()` → `.getResultStream().findFirst()`\n\nAll repositories now use JPA EntityManager directly without any Panache dependencies, making them compatible with Spring Boot while maintaining the same functionality."}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"e551caab-c624-46bd-b50e-a080c0cd7305","uuid":"9bc54a8a-f257-4986-9fe1-9be0c4c0760a"}
