{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_013rigijCDF2HAg4eedQPVAh","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\n\n## Migration Complete - Final Report\n\n### Migration Summary\nSuccessfully migrated the RealWorld (Conduit) API from **Quarkus 3.17.7** to **Spring Boot 3.4.1**. All **11/11 smoke tests pass**.\n\n### Key Changes\n| Area | Quarkus | Spring Boot |\n|------|---------|-------------|\n| REST | JAX-RS (`@Path`, `@GET`) | Spring MVC (`@RequestMapping`, `@GetMapping`) |\n| DI | CDI (`@ApplicationScoped`, `@Produces`) | Spring (`@Component`, `@Bean`, `@Configuration`) |\n| ORM | Hibernate Panache | JPA EntityManager |\n| Security | SmallRye JWT + Elytron BCrypt | jjwt + Spring Security |\n| Validation | Hibernate Validator (CDI) | Spring Boot Validation starter |\n| Error Handling | `@ServerExceptionMapper` | `@RestControllerAdvice` + `@ExceptionHandler` |\n\n### Files Modified/Created\n- **5 REST controllers** - JAX-RS to Spring MVC\n- **8 repository classes** - Panache to EntityManager\n- **5 configuration classes** - CDI to Spring `@Configuration`\n- **3 provider classes** - CDI to Spring `@Component`\n- **14 model classes** - removed `@RegisterForReflection`\n- **2 exception mappers** - JAX-RS to `@RestControllerAdvice`\n- **3 new files** - `RealWorldApiApplication.java`, `SecurityConfig.java`, `JwtAuthenticationFilter.java`\n- **1 new test file** - `smoke.py`\n- **Build/deploy** - `pom.xml`, `application.properties`, `Dockerfile`, `start.sh`\n\n### Errors Encountered & Resolved\n1. **WRAP_ROOT_VALUE on primary ObjectMapper** - List responses wrapped with class name instead of expected JSON structure. Fixed by separating into 3 ObjectMapper beans.\n2. **Missing UNWRAP_ROOT_VALUE** - Request deserialization failed for `@JsonRootName`-annotated models. Fixed by enabling `UNWRAP_ROOT_VALUE` on primary ObjectMapper.\n\n### Smoke Test Results\nAll 11 tests pass: Register, Login, Get User, Create Article, List Articles, Get Article by Slug, Create Comment, Get Comments, Get Tags, Get Profile, Favorite Article.\n\nFull details in `CHANGELOG.md`."}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":550,"cache_read_input_tokens":88984,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":550,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":589},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"e551caab-c624-46bd-b50e-a080c0cd7305","uuid":"3f90b3f9-1a91-405f-a051-c77b4ec814ce"}
{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":2427556,"duration_api_ms":2327092,"num_turns":197,"result":"---\n\n## Migration Complete - Final Report\n\n### Migration Summary\nSuccessfully migrated the RealWorld (Conduit) API from **Quarkus 3.17.7** to **Spring Boot 3.4.1**. All **11/11 smoke tests pass**.\n\n### Key Changes\n| Area | Quarkus | Spring Boot |\n|------|---------|-------------|\n| REST | JAX-RS (`@Path`, `@GET`) | Spring MVC (`@RequestMapping`, `@GetMapping`) |\n| DI | CDI (`@ApplicationScoped`, `@Produces`) | Spring (`@Component`, `@Bean`, `@Configuration`) |\n| ORM | Hibernate Panache | JPA EntityManager |\n| Security | SmallRye JWT + Elytron BCrypt | jjwt + Spring Security |\n| Validation | Hibernate Validator (CDI) | Spring Boot Validation starter |\n| Error Handling | `@ServerExceptionMapper` | `@RestControllerAdvice` + `@ExceptionHandler` |\n\n### Files Modified/Created\n- **5 REST controllers** - JAX-RS to Spring MVC\n- **8 repository classes** - Panache to EntityManager\n- **5 configuration classes** - CDI to Spring `@Configuration`\n- **3 provider classes** - CDI to Spring `@Component`\n- **14 model classes** - removed `@RegisterForReflection`\n- **2 exception mappers** - JAX-RS to `@RestControllerAdvice`\n- **3 new files** - `RealWorldApiApplication.java`, `SecurityConfig.java`, `JwtAuthenticationFilter.java`\n- **1 new test file** - `smoke.py`\n- **Build/deploy** - `pom.xml`, `application.properties`, `Dockerfile`, `start.sh`\n\n### Errors Encountered & Resolved\n1. **WRAP_ROOT_VALUE on primary ObjectMapper** - List responses wrapped with class name instead of expected JSON structure. Fixed by separating into 3 ObjectMapper beans.\n2. **Missing UNWRAP_ROOT_VALUE** - Request deserialization failed for `@JsonRootName`-annotated models. Fixed by enabling `UNWRAP_ROOT_VALUE` on primary ObjectMapper.\n\n### Smoke Test Results\nAll 11 tests pass: Register, Login, Get User, Create Article, List Articles, Get Article by Slug, Create Comment, Get Comments, Get Tags, Get Profile, Favorite Article.\n\nFull details in `CHANGELOG.md`.","session_id":"e551caab-c624-46bd-b50e-a080c0cd7305","total_cost_usd":33.36745025000002,"usage":{"input_tokens":1086,"cache_creation_input_tokens":494661,"cache_read_input_tokens":8693946,"output_tokens":72574,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":494661}},"modelUsage":{"aws/claude-3-5-haiku":{"inputTokens":276334,"outputTokens":15674,"cacheReadInputTokens":584820,"cacheCreationInputTokens":67078,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.39762679999999984,"contextWindow":200000},"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929":{"inputTokens":687,"outputTokens":72021,"cacheReadInputTokens":694374,"cacheCreationInputTokens":174019,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":1.9432594500000002,"contextWindow":200000},"aws/claude-opus-4-6":{"inputTokens":1088,"outputTokens":77258,"cacheReadInputTokens":8693946,"cacheCreationInputTokens":649332,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":31.026564000000004,"contextWindow":200000}},"permission_denials":[],"uuid":"75a9af99-f783-423a-a5ba-e4f87fd2b83b"}
